headline.main: City University Plans to Open a Graduate School of Public Health

docs.abstract: City University of New York plans to open graduate school of public health within two to three years (M)
docs.section_name: Education; Health; New York and Region
docs.lead_paragraph: The City University of New York announced yesterday that it plans to open a graduate school of public health. The university has added several schools and programs in recent years, including an honors college and a graduate journalism school.
